      "description": "A feared bounty hunter and the last of the Czarnians. Adaptational Hairstyle Change: Lobo's hair is been portrayed in several different styles across many arcs and media.On several of his own arcs he had'80s Hair.He typically defaults toBarbarian Longhair.Way back in52he was aDreadlock Warrior. He also had this hairstyle inYoung Justice.His default usual style isShōnen Hairthat seems to stand up like porcupine quills all on its own. On several of his own arcs he had'80s Hair. He typically defaults toBarbarian Longhair. Way back in52he was aDreadlock Warrior. He also had this hairstyle inYoung Justice.",
