    {
      "name": "Princess Shao-La",
      "media_title": "Lobo",
      "tropes": [
        "TheVonTropeFamily",
        "HumanAliens",
        "BraidsOfAction",
        "ChainmailBikini",
        "RebelliousPrincess"
      ],
      "description": "Braids of Action: Has a pair of twin braids and she's certainly a skilled warrior. Chainmail Bikini: Walks around in what's essentially one of this. Human Aliens: Looks just like a blonde haired woman. Rebellious Princess: She turned down the throne of her homeworld to become a thief and assassin. The Von Trope Family: Shao-LavonDarragon.",
